HEADWORD: Flos-ferri
<hw>Flos`-fer"ri</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos><ety>[L., flower of
iron.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A variety of aragonite, occurring in
